---
description: Code review checklist for Repo Risk Radar
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Flag oversized components, mixed business/UI logic, duplicated formatters, and weak typing.
- Check that deterministic security decisions remain outside OpenAI prompts.
- Check that frontend code never reads server-only secrets.
- Check that public website behavior does not execute repo code or provide offensive guidance.
- Check that deterministic logic has tests and commands were run.
